  <p id="offer-title"><i>Harmony in Darkness: AstroSentinel - Mapping Solutions for a Light-Pollution-Free Ecosystem<i></p>
  <section style="background-image: url('https://c.wallhere.com/photos/98/83/Bing_nature_landscape-2077985.jpg!d'); background-size: cover;" class="offer-item">
    <h1 id="offer-title">About</h1>
    <p>Welcome to AstroSentinel, a platform dedicated to exploring and understanding light pollution's impact on our night sky. Our mission is to provide a space where enthusiasts, researchers, and concerned citizens can come together to contribute, learn, and raise awareness about the effects of light pollution.</p>
  </section>

