        <div class="offer-item">
          <h3>1. Data Visualization</h3>
          <p> Explore interactive data visualizations depicting light pollution levels across different regions. Gain insights into the extent of artificial light and its impact on celestial visibility.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="offer-item">
          <h3>2.Contribute Your Data</h3>
          <p> Become an AstroSentinel by contributing your own light pollution measurements. Help build a comprehensive dataset to further our understanding of how artificial light affects the environment.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="offer-item">       
          <h3>3. Learn and Educate</h3>
          <p>Access resources and guides on light pollution monitoring techniques. Learn why monitoring light pollution is crucial for preserving natural ecosystems and promoting sustainable lighting practices.</p>
          </div>
    </div> 
  </section>

